# #Misfits Add - Martial Arts system locale strings

## Grant messages (shown when a style is learned)
martial-arts-learn-legion = Ave, true to Caesar! Your training in Legion Gladiatorial combat is complete.
martial-arts-learn-ranger = Your Ranger Combat Technique training pays off. Eyes forward, soldier.
martial-arts-learn-desert-survival = You've internalised the wasteland scrapper's methods. Keep moving.
martial-arts-learn-wasteland = No rules, no mercy. You know Wasteland Street Fighting now.
martial-arts-learn-tribal = Blood and sand. The Tribal Warrior style is yours.
martial-arts-learn-shadow = You understand the nerve. Shadow Strike is yours to wield.

## Already trained (shown when trying to learn a second style)
martial-arts-already-trained = You already know a martial arts form ({ $form }). You cannot learn another.

## Grab system popups
grab-soft-grab = You grab { THE($target) } loosely.
grab-hard-grab = You tighten your grip on { THE($target) }!
grab-suffocate-grab = You lock { THE($target) } in a chokehold!
grab-escaped = { THE($target) } breaks free!
grab-escape-failed = { THE($target) } can't break free yet.

## Table slam verb and popups
grab-table-slam-verb = Slam into table
grab-table-slam-pop-puller = You slam { THE($target) } into the table!
grab-table-slam-pop-target = You are slammed into the table!

